data.description: Ranch home with numerous upgrades which are sure to steal your heart. Dramatic open floor flows from dining, great room w/a fireplace & vaulted ceilings to the kitchen w/ stainless steel appliances, cherry cabinetry, arched doorways, stone backsplash & plenty of counter space. The spacious bay w/ french doors leads you to entertainers dream patio & fully fenced backyard. Brand new roof, gutters, downspouts, siding on the south side, windows, exterior light fixtures & more. Primary bedroom adorned w/crown molding, is flooded w/natural light, walk in closet which opens to ensuite bath, well appointed double vessel sinks, a separate shower & luxurious tub. Enjoy 2 add'l bedrooms, full bath & laundry room. Lower level features a full wet bar, spacious family room with brick fireplace, office with french doors, millwork and a full bath w/walk-in shower. This spacious landing offers lighted display areas, has endless possibilities w/an add'l bonus room. Close to restaurants, shopping & more!
